<div><div><h4>Job Description</h4></div><div><div><span><div><div><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></div><ul><li>Obtain actual color reading from supplier, make bardown, generate our own formula using X-rite / Pantone book or Existing data making color bardown for LAB measurement standard.</li><li>Produce huge quantity inkmix with the final approved formula.</li><li>Check all stock for expired ink every 2 weeks.</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><div><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></div><ul><li>Secondary school or High school or equivalent with previous working experience in ink room.</li><li>Good communication and interactive skills.</li><li>Knowledge of X-rite&#160; eXact and ink color matching are preferred.</li><li>Able to work with minimal supervision.</li><li>Willing to work overtime when and as necessary.</li></ul></div></span></div></div></div>
